      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Cherry Blossoms in Battle",
        "Client": "Minoto the Hub Maiden",
        "Description": "With everything that\u0027s happened\r\nin Kamura I won\u0027t feel at ease until\r\nI\u0027m strong enough to protect my\r\nsister. I failed once to protect her,\r\nbut I won\u0027t let it happen again!\r\nPlease, \u003CPL\u003E,\r\nI must become strong for Hinoa!",
        "Target": "Hunt a Mizutsune",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Cerisiers en fleur",
        "Client": "Minoto la r\u00E9ceptionniste",
        "Description": "H\u00E9, \u003CPL\u003E. J\u0027ai une\r\nfaveur \u00E0 te demander. Peux-tu\r\nm\u0027aider pour une chasse ? Je\r\ndois \u00EAtre assez forte pour\r\nprot\u00E9ger ma s\u0153ur en cas de\r\ndanger. Aide-moi \u00E0 m\u0027am\u00E9liorer\r\ns\u0027il te pla\u00EEt !",
        "Target": "Chasser un Mizutsune",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0/Temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "La caccia fa sbocciare",
        "Client": "Minoto la receptionist",
        "Description": "Ehi, \u003CPL\u003E. Posso\r\nfarti una richiesta? Vieni a\r\ncaccia con me? Devo essere\r\nabbastanza forte da proteggere\r\nmia sorella se qualche pericolo\r\ndovesse minacciare il villaggio.\r\nTi prego, aiutami a migliorare!",
        "Target": "Caccia un Mizutsune",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Kirschbl\u00FCten im Kampf",
        "Client": "Minoto das St\u00E4tten-M\u00E4del",
        "Description": "Bei allem was in Kamura passiert\r\nist, werde ich mich nicht wohl\r\nf\u00FChlen, bis ich stark genug bin,\r\nmeine Schwester zu besch\u00FCtzen.\r\nIch habe einmal versagt, nicht\r\nwieder! \u003CPL\u003E,\r\nich muss f\u00FCr Hinoa stark werden!",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Mizutsune.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Flores de cerezo en pugna",
        "Client": "Minoto de la recepci\u00F3n",
        "Description": "Con todo lo que ha sucedido en\r\nKamura, no me sentir\u00E9 c\u00F3moda\r\nhasta que pueda proteger a mi\r\nhermana. Ya fall\u00E9 en ello una\r\nvez, \u00A1no permitir\u00E9 que pase de\r\nnuevo! Por favor, \u00A1tengo que\r\nhacerme fuerte por Hinoa!",
        "Target": "Caza un Mizutsune",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
      },
      {
        "Language": "RUS",
        "Name": "\u0414\u0435\u043B\u043E \u043C\u0430\u0441\u0442\u0435\u0440\u0430 \u0431\u043E\u0438\u0442\u0441\u044F",
